            every service call.
          in: path
          name: subscriptionId
          required: true
          schema:

              value: 51766542-3ed7-4a72-a187-0c8ab644ddab

              value: 51766542-3ed7-4a72-a187-0c8ab644ddab

          in: path
          name: resourceGroupName
          required: true
          x-ms-parameter-location: method
          schema:
            type: string
            minLength: 1
            maxLength: 90
            pattern: ^[-\w\._]+$
          examples:
            List software update configuration machine run with status equal to 'Failed':
              value: mygroup
            List software update configuration machine runs:
              value: mygroup

          name: automationAccountName
          required: true

          schema:

          in: header
          name: clientRequestId
          required: false
          x-ms-parameter-location: method
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: "The filter to apply on the operation. You can use the following
            filters: 'properties/osType', 'properties/status',
            'properties/startTime', and
            'properties/softwareUpdateConfiguration/name'"
          in: query
          name: $filter
          required: false
          schema:
            type: string
          examples:
            List software update configuration machine run with status equal to 'Failed':
              value: properties/status%20eq%20'Failed'
        - description: Number of entries you skip before returning results
          in: query
          name: $skip
          required: false
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: Maximum number of entries returned in the results collection
          in: query
          name: $top
          required: false
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Return list of software update configurations runs.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/softwareUpdateConfigurationRunListResult"
              examples:
                List software update configuration machine run with status equal to 'Failed':

                    achine_run_with_status_equal_to_Failed_"

                  $ref: "#/components/examples/List_software_update_configuration_m\
                    achine_runs"
        default:
          description: Automation error response describing why the operation failed.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                description: Error response of an operation failure
                properties:
                  code:
                    description: Error code
                    type: string
                  message:
                    description: Error message indicating why the operation failed.
                    type: string
                type: object
      tags:
        - Software Update Configuration Run

        - description: The Id of the software update configuration run.
          in: path

          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            format: uuid
          examples:
            Get software update configuration runs by Id:
              value: 2bd77cfa-2e9c-41b4-a45b-684a77cfeca9
        - description: Client Api Version.

        - description: Identifies this specific client request.

          name: clientRequestId
          required: false
          x-ms-parameter-location: method
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        "200":
          description: A single software update configuration Run.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/softwareUpdateConfigurationRun"
              examples:
                Get software update configuration runs by Id:
                  $ref: "#/components/examples/Get_software_update_configuration_ru\
                    ns_by_Id"
        default:
          description: Automation error response describing why the operation failed.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                description: Error response of an operation failure
                properties:
                  code:
                    description: Error code
                    type: string
                  message:
                    description: Error message indicating why the operation failed.
                    type: string
                type: object
      tags:
